        "rich_text_9hwRAc": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Heading",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h1>The Meaning Of Toi Et Moi Rings: Two Stones, One Story </h1>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "follow_us_ygY8aG": {
          "type": "follow_us",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Follow Us on"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_ccxpK9": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Introduction ",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>In the search for rings that feel personal, meaningful, and deeply symbolic of the love of soulmates, only few match the beauty of a ‘toi et moi’ ring. Pronounced as ‘twah ay mwah’, ‘toi et moi’ is a French phrase that literally translates to ‘you and me.’ In the world of fine jewelry, toi et moi rings are one of the few designs that feel intimate and poetic. Usually, gemstone rings are chosen with just solitaire rings in mind, but the world of fine jewelry offers you with unique options such as the toi et moi <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/engagement-ring\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"engagement ring\">engagement ring</a>. Let’s first understand the meaning of toi et moi rings and then deep dive into how you can choose the right toi et moi ring for yourself easily without any confusion!</p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_kKqW7n": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "The Meaning of Toi Et Moi Rings",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>The Meaning of Toi Et Moi Rings</h2>",
            "custom_id": "the"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_yYFrht": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "The Meaning of Toi Et Paragraph",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>The ‘Toi et Moi’ ring meaning is representative of the dualities - contrasting personalities that complement each other and become whole. Each stone in this two stones ring reflects an aspect of you and your partner. Modern couples are choosing toi et moi rings because they see beyond sparkle - they see symbolism and understated luxury. This meaningful choice reflects that opposites attract or signify the similarities that bonds a couple together. Some couples even choose rings that reflect their personalities - a bold emerald paired with a soft pear diamond. Many choose stones that reflect their stories, birth months or shared milestones. After all, these two stones come together to become one story. </p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_BxFmqg": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "A Brief History of Toi et Moi Rings",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>A Brief History of Toi et Moi Rings</h3>",
            "custom_id": "a"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_wrPRca": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "A Brief History of Toi Paragraph",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Before diving into what makes a<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/toi-et-moi-engagement-rings\" target=\"_blank\" title=\" toi et moi engagement ring\"> toi et moi engagement ring</a> unique and how should you choose one, lets know the history of toi et moi rings. These rings may be trending today, but they are timeless pieces with origins steeped in centuries of romance. The most iconic and prime example dates back to 1796 when Napoleon Bonaparte proposed to Joséphine with a toi et moi ring. Back then, this devotion of love and expression took almost a rebellious form of romance for its time. Then came the Victorian Era when the popularity of these double stone rings took precedence over a single stone ring as symbolism got woven in every piece of fine jewelry crafted in that time. The trend has re-emerged in 21st century with people wanting jewelry that feels more personal, bespoke and intentionally chosen - in which diamonds are crafted to tell stories of love.</p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_Jbd43L": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "What Makes Toi Et Moi Rings Unique As Engagement Rings?",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>What Makes Toi Et Moi Rings Unique As Engagement Rings?</h2>",
            "custom_id": "what"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_zpxzBh": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Which_Should_You_Choose_e26590a1-2659-473a-b2bc-1ad085537946.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Toi et Moi rings show duality in a world that limits itself with the idea of single stone rings. This pairing of two stones that are distinct by colors, shapes or sizes, becomes the narrative of a love story. This is why two stone rings have endless customization options and you can create one that suits your love story. This is where <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Lucira Jewelry’s\">Lucira Jewelry’s</a> bespoke experience shines. With a customized toi et moi ring, you honor the nuances of your journey - what has been and what is to come - together. It is a classic, historical ring design which looks surprisingly modern, always offering a breathtaking look! The striking design of the contrasting precious stone rings look refined yet elegant, making a statement.</p>",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_PYNpgj": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Iconic Celebrity Toi Et Moi Rings ",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Iconic Celebrity Toi Et Moi Rings </h2>",
            "custom_id": "iconic"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_6JYCdt": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Megan Fox & Machine Gun Kelly",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>Megan Fox & Machine Gun Kelly</h3>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_VWDmRU": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/4_1c5c2735-0846-4fad-b11a-1918b360536b.jpg",
            "text": "<p>This iconic couple chose to combine their birthstones emerald and diamond. The magnetic bands on which the gemstones sit, intertwine to represent both individuality and union. </p>",
            "reverse_layout": true,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_BWVmEe": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Ariana Grande",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>Ariana Grande</h3>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_zwVAkV": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/5_bc3071d3-6f47-4612-982f-1764329bedca.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Ariana Grande’s gasp worthy is a stunning pairing of an oval diamond and a lustrous pearl. Her ring features a combination of modern brilliance with emotional heritage. This sensational ring is an epitome of a Toi et Moi ring.</p>",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_bPLMNC": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Kylie Jenner",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>Kylie Jenner</h3>",
            "custom_id": "classic"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_NwRy9R": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/6_fa23b6a8-0c9e-44e9-b389-07d401e75011.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Kylie Jenner’s toi et moi ring stirred the social media with matching toi et moi rings for herself and her daughter Stormi Webster reportedly by Travis Scott. This stands as a prime example for the idea that a ‘couple’s’ definition goes beyond romantic partners, and can extend to mothers and daughters, or any special bond for that matter. </p>",
            "reverse_layout": true,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_TbC4mN": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "How To Choose A Toi Et Moi Ring?",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>How To Choose A Toi Et Moi Ring?</h2><p>Selecting a toi et moi ring is a beautiful process. You come across thought provoking doubts and we are here to help you out with a step by step process to choose a toi et moi ring!</p>",
            "custom_id": "how"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_jMYfry": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Step 1: Choose Your Story, Then The Diamonds",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>Step 1: Choose Your Story, Then The Diamonds</h3>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_RyRAtY": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Every diamond jewelry looks stunning, but it becomes even more beautiful when it is symbolic of your story. First discuss with your partner what you want the stories to represent. - two personalities, two birth months, two favorite gems or even two cuts that you were confused about while choosing a solitaire and so are now choosing a toi et moi ring! Let the meaning guide the design rather than the other way around.</p>",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_CbXLkg": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Step 2: Balance the cuts",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>Step 2: Balance the cuts</h3>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_iiFrKE": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/7_8912f9a5-5de4-4b6e-92bc-9f662ef18fcb.jpg",
            "text": "<p>The beauty of two stone rings lies in the harmony of the two when they are set together. Some combinations pair naturally, making them the most preferred combinations when it comes to toi et moi rings: pear and round, <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/products/pear-emerald-cut-solitaire-ring\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"emerald and pear cut \">emerald and pear cut </a>, oval and cushion and <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/products/marquise-round-toi-et-moi-ring\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"marquise and round cut \">marquise and round cut </a>. Find the pair that goes well with the aesthetic you want. </p>",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_hEAXhx": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Step 3: Consider the proportion ",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>Step 3: Consider the proportion </h3>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_NiGrXL": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/8_0f175032-32be-4047-94c3-0033e77bf139.jpg",
            "text": "<p>It is not necessary for both the stones to be of the same size. In fact, the difference in size is often preferred to balance the proportion. Choosing a scale that avoids imbalance and balance itself can enhance the visual appeal of  a toi et moi ring. </p>",
            "reverse_layout": true,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_cTfgNx": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Step 4: Choose the metal and setting",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>Step 4: Choose the metal and setting</h3>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_NN3FF4": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/9_41337834-d136-49b2-87aa-95316df739e4.jpg",
            "text": "<p>White gold, platinum, yellow gold, and rose gold can dramatically alter the overall character. Choose yellow gold if you are choosing colored diamonds to make the color pop even better! When you are seeking a look that adds warmth and romance, choose rose gold while platinum and white gold both offer a sleek look with a luxury finish.</p>",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_nAhVjq": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Step 4: Choose the  Paragraph",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p> With the metal, choose a setting that maintains the harmony of the diamonds and the metal. All these elements need to synchronize so as to look one, so as to look whole! </p><p>While making any choice, research beyond the look! Consider lifestyle and longevity and look for jewellers that focus on craftsmanship and durability. A well crafted toi et moi ring looks seamless, two stones, one story, zero compromise on comfort or safety.</p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_3fBN74": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Conclusion ",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Conclusion </h2><p>The Toi Et Moi ring is more than a design trend, it is a centuries old symbol of connection, destiny and individuality. For modern couples, it offers the perfect blend of heritage and contemporary elegance. We believe every ring has a story to say but none do it as beautifully and poetically as a toi et moi ring does. </p>",
            "custom_id": "conclusion"
          }
        }
      },
